item.title: 21116PCN_HeidiSpencer
item.description: 21116, LOS CABOS, MEXICO - Thursday April 10 2008. **EXCLUSIVE** During their romantic vacation in Mexico, reality TV stars Heidi Montag and Spencer Pratt enjoy a trip to the beach. The couple, who shot to fame in the reality show "The Hills", were seen chatting and relaxing in the warm, Mexican sun. The couple read magazines, including the Forbes Rich List, as they drank champagne and kissed at the Palmilla Resort in Los Cabos.
